//wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/appcloner" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>AppCloner</strong></em></a>: How to use App Cloner to have modded and unmodded Go app on same device.</li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/apkdesconstruct" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>apkdesconstruct</strong></em></a>: Taking apart the APK file manually</li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/googlemaps" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>GoogleMaps</strong></em></a>: Get google maps working in the patched APK file</li></ul><h3 id="battery-information" tabindex="-1">Battery Information <a href="#battery_information" id="battery_information"></a> <a class="header-anchor" href="#battery-information" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Battery Information &lt;a href=&quot;#battery_information&quot; id=&quot;battery_information&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&quot;">​</a></h3><ul><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/batfirmfailed" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>batfirmfailed</strong></em></a>: How to fix Mavics battery if it got broken due to failed firmware update</li><li></li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/comm_sbs_bqctrl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>comm_sbs_bqctrl</strong></em></a>: Smart Battery System I2C/SMBus communication tool.</li></ul><h3 id="crystalsky" tabindex="-1">CrystalSky <a href="#crystalsky" id="crystalsky"></a> <a class="header-anchor" href="#crystalsky" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;CrystalSky &lt;a href=&quot;#crystalsky&quot; id=&quot;crystalsky&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&quot;">​</a></h3><ul><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/crystalsky" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>crystalsky</strong></em></a>: How to root and modify CrystalSky</li></ul><h3 id="dji-assistant" tabindex="-1">DJI Assistant <a href="#dji_assistant" id="dji_assistant"></a> <a class="header-anchor" href="#dji-assistant" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;DJI Assistant &lt;a href=&quot;#dji_assistant&quot; id=&quot;dji_assistant&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&quot;">​</a></h3><ul><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/download_assistant" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>Download Assistant</strong></em></a>: Download links for DJI Assistant 2</li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/app.asar" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>app.asar</strong></em></a>: How to extract and explore the DJI Assistant code</li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/using_frida_with_assistant_app" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>Using FRIDA with Assistant App</strong></em></a>: Look at Assistant.app and Assistant.exe mods</li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/assistanddebug" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>assistanddebug</strong></em></a>: How to enable debugging on assistant 1.1.2 or earlier (allows unlocking parameters)</li></ul><h3 id="dji-goggles" tabindex="-1">DJI Goggles <a href="#dji_goggles" id="dji_goggles"></a> <a class="header-anchor" href="#dji-goggles" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;DJI Goggles &lt;a href=&quot;#dji_goggles&quot; id=&quot;dji_goggles&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&quot;">​</a></h3><ul><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/gogglevideos" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>gogglevideos</strong></em></a>: Play videos on DJI Goggles</li></ul><h3 id="droneid" tabindex="-1">DroneID <a href="#droneid" id="droneid"></a> <a class="header-anchor" href="#droneid" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;DroneID &lt;a href=&quot;#droneid&quot; id=&quot;droneid&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&quot;">​</a></h3><ul><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/cia_jeep_doors" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>CIA Jeep Doors</strong></em></a>: CIAJeepDoors tool to remove DroneID from DJI Aircraft</li></ul><h3 id="fcc-mods" tabindex="-1">FCC Mods <a href="#fcc_mods" id="fcc_mods"></a> <a class="header-anchor" href="#fcc-mods" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;FCC Mods &lt;a href=&quot;#fcc_mods&quot; id=&quot;fcc_mods&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&quot;">​</a></h3><ul><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/dji_configs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>FCC-Hack</strong></em></a>: Some config hacks to change radio transmission settings for those outside the USA</li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/jkson_fcc_mod" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>jkson FCC mod</strong></em></a>: For forcing Mavic Pro or P4Pv2 SDR settings such as FCC, Boost, force_2.3G or force_2.5G</li></ul><h3 id="firmware-modding" tabindex="-1">Firmware Modding <a href="#firmware_modding" id="firmware_modding"></a> <a class="header-anchor" href="#firmware-modding" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Firmware Modding &lt;a href=&quot;#firmware_modding&quot; id=&quot;firmware_modding&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&quot;">​</a></h3><p><strong>How TO&#39;s</strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/parameterhacks" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>parameterhacks</strong></em></a>: Parameter Hacks - Simple guide to changing some parameters, including recommended values. (Mavic Series, p4 series, Inspire 2, Spark)</li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/modulemix" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>modulemix</strong></em></a>: How to mix firmware modules and flash them (Mavic Series, p4 series, Inspire 2, Spark)</li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/fc_patcher_tool" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>FC Patcher Tool</strong></em></a>: Modify flight controller parameters on the the LATEST DJI firmware (Mavic Series, p4 series, Inspire 2, Spark)</li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/manually_installing_custom_fw_from_fc_patcher" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>Manually Installing Custom FW from FC Patcher</strong></em></a>: Manual steps to install custom firmware after its been created from the FC Patcher tool.</li><li><a href="https://wiki.dji-rev.com/howto/super-patcher" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><em><strong>Super-Patcher</